    <item>
      <title>2022 年初，Instagram 贡献了 Meta 近 30% 的收入</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/instagram-generated-almost-30-of-meta-s-revenue-in-early-2022</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法庭文件显示，2022 年上半年，Meta Platforms Inc. 近 30% 的收入来自 Instagram，该文件首次披露了流行的照片和视频服务的收入。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/instagram-generated-almost-30-of-meta-s-revenue-in-early-2022</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 18:57:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>就业数据和苹果裁员|彭博科技</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-05/jobs-data-and-apple-layoffs-bloomberg-technology</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着美国就业报告的发布，彭博社的卡罗琳·海德和埃德·勒德洛了解了科技劳动力市场的健康状况。此外，新的文件显示，苹果在取消汽车和屏幕项目后裁减了约 600 个职位，Meta 也改变了一些政策，允许更多人工智能生成的内容保留在其平台上。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-05/jobs-data-and-apple-layoffs-bloomberg-technology</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 18:37:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Meta 要求法官在审判前驳回 FTC 反垄断案件</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/meta-asks-judge-to-throw-out-ftc-antitrust-case-before-trial</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Meta Platforms Inc.请求法官驳回美国联邦贸易委员会寻求分拆该公司的反垄断诉讼，称该机构无法证明如果不收购Instagram和WhatsApp，消费者的生活会更好。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/meta-asks-judge-to-throw-out-ftc-antitrust-case-before-trial</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 18:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>MicroStrategy 预计比特币在上涨 150% 后减半会带来更多收益</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/microstrategy-mstr-eyes-more-gains-on-bitcoin-halving-after-150-rally</link>
      <description><![CDATA[MicroStrategy Inc. 飙升 150%——由对比特币的大赌注驱动—— BTIG 分析师表示，随着加密货币的飙升，其还有进一步攀升的空间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/microstrategy-mstr-eyes-more-gains-on-bitcoin-halving-after-150-rally</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 17:13:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Meta 停止删除一些人工智能生成的帖子，即使具有误导性</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/meta-to-label-more-ai-generated-posts-instead-of-removing-them</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Facebook 和 Instagram 的母公司 Meta Platforms Inc. 正在改变其政策，以允许更多人工智能生成的内容保留在其网站上，即使这些内容具有误导性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/meta-to-label-more-ai-generated-posts-instead-of-removing-them</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 14:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国监管机构暂停罚款，威胁泰晤士水务的未来</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/uk-watchdog-stalls-on-fine-that-threatens-thames-water-s-future</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着伦敦自来水供应商陷入更深的危机，英国监管机构正在犹豫是否对该公司处以罚款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/uk-watchdog-stalls-on-fine-that-threatens-thames-water-s-future</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 13:49:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Ares 牵头 CentralSquare 12 亿美元再融资交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/ares-leads-1-2-billion-refinancing-deal-for-centralsquare</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，以 Ares Management Corp. 为首的私人信贷公司正在向软件开发商 CentralSquare Technologies 提供超过 12 亿美元的债务方案，为其债务再融资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/ares-leads-1-2-billion-refinancing-deal-for-centralsquare</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 21:07:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>YouTube 表示 OpenAI 通过其视频训练 Sora 会违反规则</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/youtube-says-openai-training-sora-with-its-videos-would-break-the-rules</link>
      <description><![CDATA[YouTube 首席执行官 Neal Mohan 表示，使用 YouTube 视频来训练 OpenAI 的文本到视频生成器将违反该平台的服务条款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/youtube-says-openai-training-sora-with-its-videos-would-break-the-rules</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 18:54:54 GMT</pubDate>
